.TH "STX CONFIG" "1" "2026-04-19" "0.1.0" "stx config Manual"
.SH NAME
stx\-config \- Inspect merged effective configuration...
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B stx config
[OPTIONS] COMMAND [ARGS]...
.SH DESCRIPTION
Inspect merged effective configuration (flag > env > file > defaults).
.SH COMMANDS
.PP
\fBshow\fP
  Print merged, validated config as YAML.
  See \fBstx config-show(1)\fP for full documentation on the \fBshow\fP command.
.PP
\fBdiff\fP
  Print keys that differ from Pydantic...
  See \fBstx config-diff(1)\fP for full documentation on the \fBdiff\fP command.
